lambda}})$, finding an $\\alpha$-approximate minimum cut\nin networks of edge connectivity $\\lambda$ or computing an\n$\\alpha$-approximation of the edge connectivity requires $\\tilde{\\Omega}(D +\n\\sqrt{\\frac{n}{\\alpha\\lambda}})$ rounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 May 2013 19:13:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2013 19:16:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-21"}
