ulation leads galaxy formation to become effectively\nstochastic on mass scales of M_h ~ 10^10 Msun, and thus these massive dwarfs\nare not \"too big to fail\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 May 2013 20:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2013 19:01:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
