c. As a corollary we prove that if\n$\\gamma(G) \\geq 4$ and $\\chi \\leq -1$, then $b(G) \\leq 11 - 24\\chi/(9 +\n\\sqrt{41 - 8\\chi})$. Several unanswered questions are posed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 May 2013 11:32:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-27"}
