 that in an active region the field-line braiding is the dominant\nheating process, at least at the spatial scales available to current\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 May 2013 11:35:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 22 Jun 2014 16:05:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Sep 2017 00:30:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-19"}
